            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Gradually whisk the <strong>beef stock</strong> into the <strong>roux</strong>, a little at a time, and cook for 5 min or until a smooth, thick sauce remains – this is your <strong>gravy dip</strong></p><p>Tip: If your gravy isn't thickening, increase the heat to high and leave to bubble away!</p>",
